lagrange (1.20.8-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Rewrote packaging for cross-arch builds: dh_auto_configure/dh_auto_build
    now drive CMake instead of calling cmake directly, so DEB_HOST_ARCH-aware
    toolchain files get injected automatically during cross builds.
  * Switched from vendoring the_Foundation as an internal static library to
    linking the libtfdn-dev package.
  * Split into three binary packages: lagrange-common (architecture-
    independent resources), lagrange (GUI), and lagrange-curses-tui (TUI).
  * Bumped to debhelper-compat 13.

 -- Jaakko Keränen (skyjake) <jaakko.keranen@iki.fi>  Sun, 21 Jun 2026 06:26:17 +0300
